{"title":"一步一步搭建Wooyun镜像站","date":"2019-08-01T01:34:44.739Z","slug":"build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step","comments":true,"updated":"2019-08-01T01:50:30.398Z","content":"<h3 id=\"0x00：下载Wooyun镜像\">0x00：下载Wooyun镜像<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0x00：下载Wooyun镜像\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/hanc00l/wooyun_public\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">镜像仓库</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"0x01：下载并安装VMWare虚拟机\">0x01：下载并安装VMWare虚拟机<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0x01：下载并安装VMWare虚拟机\"></a></h3><h3 id=\"0x02：解压并用VMware虚拟机打开解压后的镜像\">0x02：解压并用VMware虚拟机打开解压后的镜像<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0x02：解压并用VMware虚拟机打开解压后的镜像\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li>将虚拟机重启后重新获取IP地址</li>\n<li>输入用户名hancool和密码qwe123</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"0x03：运行Elasticsearch全文检索\">0x03：运行Elasticsearch全文检索<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0x03：运行Elasticsearch全文检索\"></a></h3><p>进入虚拟机<code>elasticsearch-2.3.4/bin</code>目录下运行<code>./elasticsearch -d</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"0x04：运行Wooyun主程序\">0x04：运行Wooyun主程序<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0x04：运行Wooyun主程序\"></a></h3><p>进入<code>wooyun_public/flask</code>目录，运行<code>./app.py</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"0x05：使用Wooyun镜像\">0x05：使用Wooyun镜像<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0x05：使用Wooyun镜像\"></a></h3><p>打开浏览器，输入<a href=\"http://ip:5000，ip为虚拟机的网卡地址\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://ip:5000，ip为虚拟机的网卡地址</a>(使用<code>ifconfig eth0</code>查看)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/images/wooyun-mirror.png\" alt=\"Wooyun\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"0xFF：常见错误\">0xFF：常见错误<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#0xFF：常见错误\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"安装后搜索报500\">安装后搜索报500<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#安装后搜索报500\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>进入<code>elasticsearch-2.3.4/bin</code>目录下运行<code>./elasticsearch -d</code> (-d表示以后台方式运行)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"搜索结果超过500页报500错误\">搜索结果超过500页报500错误<a href=\"post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step#搜索结果超过500页报500错误\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>elasticsearch默认的最大分页数是10000条记录(也就是500页)，因此超过500页会报错。</li>\n<li><p>修改默认最大分页记录</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -XPUT <span class=\"string\">\"http://localhost:9200/wooyun/_settings\"</span> -d <span class=\"string\">'&#123; \"index\" : &#123; \"max_result_window\" : 500000 &#125; &#125;'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"致敬Wooyun！\"><a href=\"#致敬Wooyun！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"致敬Wooyun！\"></a>致敬Wooyun！</h2></li>\n</ul>\n","next":{"title":"PHP手工注入以及通过SqlMap自动注入基本语法","slug":"php-injection-by-sqlmap-and-custom"},"link":"https://www.alipay.one/post/build-wooyun-mirror-bugs-drops-step-by-step/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"致敬Wooyun！","index":"1"}]}